{"tid":1701654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府同差佬眼中既法治係咪只係市民聽哂佢地講野就得？","createTime":"2019-11-09T07:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T09:05:58.000Z","uid":73972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4124a56ac9885c72e66c12c4a268b8b8728d0997","tid":1701654,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"政府同差佬成日鬧示威者破壞法治，但如果示威者做違法野，有人會拉佢地、檢控佢地、送佢地上法庭審、判左有罪會有刑罰，成個過程都好「法治」<br />\n<br />\n相反，而加律政司選擇性檢控、同類型案件處理「親」「疏」有別，差佬濫捕、打壓異己、護短、執法不公，政府滿口謊言、愚民愚己，法庭藍官比比皆是、中立客觀性成疑，咁破壞法治既唔係港府同所有體制下既一班人？政府仲可以咁厚顏無恥叫人相信法治？<br />\n<br />\n香港所謂自豪既司法系統同法治只係假象，惺惺作態，一場運動、一個考驗就已經揭破香港成個司法系統既假面具，面具底下表現出既全部係偏頗政府、維穩、不公義同殘民既工具"},{"pid":"11320e984e9294f2e2c42cdd7ac0e940b5f4b840","tid":1701654,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gb0BsVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgb0BsVw.jpg&h=f2aff6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總部: <a href=\"http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=95720068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍西分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=063ac936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A</a><br />\n九龍東分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOC%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=77552436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw</a><br />\n新界東分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRKBT8rgAIkf-Z1FjQ\" data-sr-url=\"h